'''YouTube'''（舊稱'''YouTube聚光燈'''）是[[YouTube|YouTube]]自办的官方频道。正如其舊稱的意思，该频道用于聚焦YouTube上的影片和活动。获得该频道关注的活动包括{{le|YouTube喜剧週|YouTube Comedy Week}}和[[YouTube音乐奖|YouTube音乐奖]]。此外，频道会上传《YouTube国度》和一年一度的[[YouTube年度回顧|YouTube年度回顧]]。

2013年11月2日，YouTube频道暂时超越[[PewDiePie|PewDiePie]]频道，成为该站[[在YouTube上訂閱人數最多的用戶列表|订阅人数最多的频道]]。新用户注册YouTube时，该频道作为订阅选项，透过自动建议和预选择登上头位<ref>{{cite web|last=Cohen|first=Joshua|url=http://www.tubefilter.com/2013/11/04/youtube-most-susbcribed-channel|title=YouTube Is Now The Most Subscribed Channel On YouTube|publisher=''Tubefilter''|date=2013-11-04|accessdate=2013-09-20|archive-date=2019-06-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190611220943/https://www.tubefilter.com/2013/11/04/youtube-most-susbcribed-channel/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2013年12月，该频道与PewDiePie的榜首位置之争激烈，直到12月22日被PewDiePie稳拿头名。截至2020年8月4日，该频道已赢得3060万订阅户，影片被观看22.9多亿次<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.youtube.com/user/YouTube/about|title=YouTube about|publisher=YouTube|accessdate=2014-09-20|archive-date=2013-12-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131222042047/https://www.youtube.com/user/YouTube/about|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

== 视频 ==
YouTube近期常透過該頻道宣傳、推廣[[2019冠状病毒病|Covid-19]]的防疫觀念、種族不公的對話影片和[[一日一生_(2021年電影)|群眾外包紀錄片]]計畫等。

=== YouTube年度回顾 ===
{{Main|YouTube年度回顧}}
自2010年以来，YouTube透过聚光灯频道发布一年一度的[[YouTube年度回顧|YouTube年度回顧]]视频。2013年视频在聚光灯频道上的宣传攻势，帮助2013版节目仅在数小时内便被观看100多万次<ref>{{cite web|last=Gutelle|first=Sam|url=http://www.tubefilter.com/2013/12/11/youtube-rewind-2013-what-does-youtube-say-portal-a/|title=With Over 50 Cameos, YouTube Rewind 2013 Is Even Bigger Than 2012|publisher=''Tubefilter''|date=2013-12-11|accessdate=2014-09-20|archive-date=2014-04-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140408214853/http://www.tubefilter.com/2013/12/11/youtube-rewind-2013-what-does-youtube-say-portal-a/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。[[Google|Google]]曾发表文章详述2013年间的[[网络搜索引擎|搜索引擎]]和人们在YouTube上看过的视频，文中附上当年的回顾视频<ref>{{cite web|url=http://googleblog.blogspot.com/2013/12/youtube-rewind-what-you-watched-in-2013.html|title=YouTube Rewind: What you watched in 2013|publisher=''Blogspot''|work=Official Google Blog|date=2013-12-11|accessdate=2014-09-20|archive-date=2020-09-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200903070346/https://googleblog.blogspot.com/2013/12/youtube-rewind-what-you-watched-in-2013.html}}</ref>。

=== YouTube国度 ===
《YouTube国度》（{{lang|en|''YouTube Nation''}}）是YouTube与[[梦工厂动画|梦工厂动画]]的合作项目，于2014年1月在其自有频道上线<ref>{{cite web|url=http://deadline.com/2014/01/dreamworks-animation-youtube-nation-663833/|title=DreamWorks Animation Confirms Daily YouTube Show ‘YouTube Nation’|publisher=''Deadline''|date=2014-01-13|accessdate=2014-09-20|archive-date=2019-06-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190624073359/https://deadline.com/2014/01/dreamworks-animation-youtube-nation-663833/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。梦工厂负责监督制作，YouTube管理节目的销售和营销<ref>{{cite web|last=Wallenstein|first=Andrew|url=http://variety.com/2014/digital/news/new-series-youtube-nation-launches-tuesday-from-youtube-dreamworks-animation-1201053518/|title=New Series ‘YouTube Nation’ Launches Tuesday on YouTube via DreamWorks Animation|publisher=''Variety''|date=2014-01-13|accessdate=2015-04-06|archive-date=2021-10-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211006091935/https://variety.com/2014/digital/news/new-series-youtube-nation-launches-tuesday-from-youtube-dreamworks-animation-1201053518/}}</ref>。该节目是集合聚光灯频道信息的新闻系列<ref>{{cite web|last=Gutelle|first=Sam|url=http://www.tubefilter.com/2014/01/09/youtube-nation-dreamworks-daily-news-show/|title=YouTube And Dreamworks To Launch Daily Video News Show|publisher=''Tubefilter''|date=2014-01-09|accessdate=2014-09-20|archive-date=2019-06-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190616131828/https://www.tubefilter.com/2014/01/09/youtube-nation-dreamworks-daily-news-show/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。YouTube也会透过聚光灯频道推广该节目。在它早期的历史中，节目起用[[格雷斯·赫尔比希|格雷斯·赫尔比希]]、{{le|汉娜·哈特|Hannah Hart}}和{{le|玛姆丽·哈特|Mamrie Hart}}嘉宾协助推广节目及其观众<ref>{{cite web|last=Gutelle|first=Sam|url=http://www.tubefilter.com/2014/02/11/grace-helbig-hannah-hart-mamrie-hart-youtube-nation/|title=Grace Helbig, Hannah Hart, And Mamrie Hart Take Over ‘YouTube Nation’|publisher=''Tubefilter''|date=2014-02-11|accessdate=2014-09-20|archive-date=2019-06-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190630042231/https://www.tubefilter.com/2014/02/11/grace-helbig-hannah-hart-mamrie-hart-youtube-nation/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

由于经常在聚光灯频道上推广，节目上线三个月内便迈入100万订阅用户大关<ref>{{cite web|last=Gutelle|first=Sam|url=http://www.tubefilter.com/2014/04/17/youtube-millionaires-nation-steve-woolf-zadi-diaz/|title=YouTube Millionaires: YouTube Nation Finds The Best Videos On The Net|publisher=''Tubefilter''|date=2014-04-17|accessdate=2014-09-20|archive-date=2019-06-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190612235838/https://www.tubefilter.com/2014/04/17/youtube-millionaires-nation-steve-woolf-zadi-diaz/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。节目被提名为第4届{{le|最佳播客奖|Streamy Award}}的最佳新闻和时事节目奖，但最终输给了{{le|SourceFed|SourceFed}}<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.streamys.org/nominees-winners/4th-annual-nominees-winners/|title=4th Annual Streamy Awards Nominees|publisher=''Streamys''|accessdate=2014-09-20|archive-date=2014-09-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140924123852/http://www.streamys.org/nominees-winners/4th-annual-nominees-winners/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。在播出350集后，节目于2014年12月5日收播<ref>{{cite web|last=Spangler|first=Todd|url=http://variety.com/2014/digital/news/dreamworks-animation-youtube-pull-plug-on-youtube-nation-show-1201370036/|title=DreamWorks Animation, YouTube Pull Plug on ‘YouTube Nation’ Show|publisher=''Variety''|date=2014-12-04|accessdate=2015-01-09|archive-date=2022-04-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220419050330/https://variety.com/2014/digital/news/dreamworks-animation-youtube-pull-plug-on-youtube-nation-show-1201370036/}}</ref>。

== 活动 ==
=== 主题週活动 ===
2013年5月，聚光灯频道用于流转播由{{le|ChannelFlip|ChannelFlip}}制作的{{le|YouTube喜剧周|YouTube Comedy Week|喜剧周活动}}。活动期间，YouTube利用主页聚焦专门为活动制作的戏剧视频<ref>{{cite web|last=Rothman|first=Lily|url=http://entertainment.time.com/2013/05/20/youtube-bets-big-on-laughs-with-its-first-ever-comedy-week/|title=YouTube Bets Big on Laughs with Its First-Ever "Comedy Week"|publisher=''TIME''|date=2013-05-20|accessdate=2014-09-20|archive-date=2019-06-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190605010243/http://entertainment.time.com/2013/05/20/youtube-bets-big-on-laughs-with-its-first-ever-comedy-week/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。两小时首播仪式视频截至2014年9月已获得106万次观看<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=5z3cI0NnKN0|title=The Big Live Comedy Show - YouTube Comedy Week|publisher=YouTube|date=2013-05-19|accessdate=2014-09-20|archive-date=2019-06-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190609215944/https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=5z3cI0NnKN0|dead-url=no}}</ref>。活动获得的评价好坏参半，传统媒体和新媒体名人的特别融合以及技术难题被专门挑剔。活动是YouTube流转播的首个喜剧节目<ref>{{cite web|last=Gutelle|first=Sam|url=http://www.tubefilter.com/2013/05/20/youtube-big-live-comedy-show-fail/|title=Six Reasons Why YouTube’s ‘Big Live Comedy Show’ Didn’t Work|publisher=''Tubefilter''|date=2013-05-20|accessdate=2014-09-20|archive-date=2019-06-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190611121037/https://www.tubefilter.com/2013/05/20/youtube-big-live-comedy-show-fail/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。尽管活动被宣传为第一届喜剧週活动，但往后的活动杳无音讯。

2013年8月4日，YouTube推出由[[美国|美国]]华裔{{le|黄谷子|Freddie Wong}}和英国人Tomska创办的“极客週”（{{lang|en|Geek Week}}）<ref name=ytgeekweek>{{cite web|url=http://youtube-global.blogspot.com/2013/07/youtube-geekweek-2013.html|title=YouTube geeks out with first-ever Geek Week: August 4-10, 2013|publisher=''Blogspot''|work=YouTube Official Blog|date=2013-07-24|accessdate=2014-09-20|archive-date=2015-12-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151202074047/http://youtube-global.blogspot.com/2013/07/youtube-geekweek-2013.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|last=Gutelle|first=Sam|url=http://www.tubefilter.com/2013/07/24/youtube-geek-week-teaser/|title=Geek Week Officially Coming August 4th As YouTube Releases Teaser|publisher=''Tubefilter''|date=2013-07-24|accessdate=2014-09-20|archive-date=2019-06-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190629134114/https://www.tubefilter.com/2013/07/24/youtube-geek-week-teaser/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。该週由各个主题日组成，包括一鸣惊人星期天（{{lang|en|Blockbuster Sunday}}）、全球极客星期一（{{lang|en|Global Geekery Monday}}）、智囊团星期二（{{lang|en|Brainiac Tuesday}}）、超级星期三（{{lang|en|Super Wednesday}}）、游戏星期四（{{lang|en|Gaming Thursday}}）和粉丝星期五（{{lang|en|Fan Friday}}）。活动由{{le|德斯特实业公司|Nerdist|德斯特}}和ChannelFlip分别在美国和英国联合推出<ref>{{cite web|last=Cohen|first=Matt|url=http://www.nerdist.com/2013/07/youtube-launches-geek-week/|title=YouTube Launches "Geek Week"|publisher=''Nerdist''|date=2013-07-24|accessdate=2014-09-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140429004959/http://www.nerdist.com/2013/07/youtube-launches-geek-week/|archive-date=2014-04-29|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|last=Schroeder|first=Stan|url=http://mashable.com/2013/07/24/youtube-geek-week/|title=YouTube Announces Geek Week, Starting Aug. 4|publisher=''Mashable''|date=2013-07-24|accessdate=2014-09-20|archive-date=2019-06-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190613034932/https://mashable.com/2013/07/24/youtube-geek-week/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

=== #ProudToLove ===
2013年[[同性戀自豪日|同志骄傲月]]期间，频道被用来关注同志及其相关资讯和视频<ref>{{cite web|last=Rudolph|first=Christopher|url=http://www.huffingtonpost.com/2013/06/27/youtube-proud-to-love_n_3511805.html|title=YouTube Celebrates Gay Pride With 'Proud To Love' (VIDEO)|publisher=''Huffington Post''|date=2013-06-27|accessdate=2014-09-20|archive-date=2016-03-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304130912/http://www.huffingtonpost.com/2013/06/27/youtube-proud-to-love_n_3511805.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。YouTube母公司[[谷歌|谷歌]]被记载为同性恋冠军<ref>{{cite web|last=Crook|first=Jordan|url=http://techcrunch.com/2013/06/27/youtube-celebrates-pride-with-proudtolove-spotlight-channel/|title=YouTube Celebrates Pride With #ProudToLove Spotlight Channel|publisher=''Tech Crunch''|date=2013-06-27|accessdate=2014-09-20|archive-date=2020-08-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200819152230/https://techcrunch.com/2013/06/27/youtube-celebrates-pride-with-proudtolove-spotlight-channel/}}</ref>。YouTube官方博客发表了一篇跟活动有关的文章<ref>{{cite web|url=http://youtube-global.blogspot.com/2013/06/were-proudtolove-lgbt-community-on.html|title=We’re #ProudToLove the LGBT community on YouTube|publisher=''Blogspot''|work=YouTube Official Blog|date=2013-06-27|accessdate=2014-09-20|archive-date=2015-10-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151029175512/http://youtube-global.blogspot.com/2013/06/were-proudtolove-lgbt-community-on.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

=== YouTube音乐奖 ===
{{main|YouTube音乐奖}}
2013年11月，YouTube举办首屆[[YouTube音乐奖|音乐奖颁奖典礼]]。各项提名提前一个月揭晓，颁奖典礼旨在透过社交媒体投票模式创造流量<ref>{{cite web|last=Spangler|first=Todd|url=http://variety.com/2013/digital/news/youtube-music-awards-nominees-announced-1200749352/|title=YouTube Music Awards Nominees Announced|publisher=''Variety''|date=2013-10-21|accessdate=2013-09-20|archive-date=2015-07-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150727153157/http://variety.com/2013/digital/news/youtube-music-awards-nominees-announced-1200749352/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。活动在聚光灯频道上流转播，截至2014年9月已获得450多万次播放<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=yXBPbnv1H-U|title=The First-Ever YouTube Music Awards (YTMA)|publisher=''YouTube''|date=2013-11-05|accessdate=2013-09-20|archive-date=2019-06-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190618152409/https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=yXBPbnv1H-U|dead-url=no}}</ref>。活动的技术难题和主流艺人提名占大多数取代YouTube艺人成为口诛笔伐的焦点<ref>{{cite web|last=Gelt|first=Jessica|url=http://www.latimes.com/entertainment/tv/showtracker/la-et-st-youtube-music-awards-eminem-wins-artist-of-the-year-20131103-story.html#axzz2jdsdyvQY|title=YouTube Music Awards: Eminem wins Artist of the Year ... wait, what?|publisher=''Los Angeles Times''|date=2013-11-03|accessdate=2013-09-20|archive-date=2019-06-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190629003917/https://www.latimes.com/entertainment/tv/showtracker/la-et-st-youtube-music-awards-eminem-wins-artist-of-the-year-20131103-story.html#axzz2jdsdyvQY|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

